node.text:
It’s game time with @laceclips. 💯

I’m proud to announce that I’ve joined the @laceclips All-Star Roster. Their wearable tracker locks into your laces to monitor your movement & track your performance stats. Ideal for anyone wanting to improve their game, it syncs with app to track your progress and you can even compete and compare your performance against friends or pro athletes. Available for pre-order today. Get yours & show me what you got!! #laceup #LaceClipsAthlete
